sql:
SELECT total_attendance
FROM attendance
ORDER BY total_attendance DESC;

SELECT AVG(wait_time) AS average_wait_time
FROM wait_times
WHERE date_id = 123;

external_knowledge:
- This question assumes that a higher wait time rank indicates a longer wait time; 
- Weather conditions can significantly impact park attendance and wait times; 
- Holidays may also influence the number of visitors and wait times at parks.
